Class Concept

java.lang.Object

      dhbw.LWBS.CA5_KB1.model.Concept
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<Person>
public class Concept
extends Person

This is a specification of the class Person. In contrast to a Person a Concept doesn't contain a number or a book. Besides a Concept can be either specialized or generalized.
